      "text": "X; \"near\")\n\n[](https://en.mfa.gov.ir/ \"Return\")\n\n[](https://en.mfa.gov.ir/portal/newsview/791053/Foreign-Ministry-Spokesperson-explains-FMs-Saturday-visit-to-Oman#mega-menu)\n\n[](javascript:void(0); \"Search\")\n\n[](javascript:void(0); \"زبان \")\n\nفارسی\n\nعربی\n\n[](javascript:void(0); \"Font size\")\n\n[](javascript:void(0);)\n\nAbout us\n\n* Minister \"Minister\")\n\n* Minister of Foreign Affairs\n\n* Office of Deputies \"Office of Deputies\")\n\n* Legal & International Affairs\n\n* Economic Diplomacy\n\n* Political Affairs\n\n* Consular, Parliamentary, Iranian Expat Affairs\n\n* Administrative and Financial Affairs\n\n* Center for Public Diplomacy\n\n* Institute for Political and International Studies\n\n* Overview \"Overview\")\n\n* IRI Flag\n\n* IRI National Anthem\n\n* Minister\n\n* Office of Deputies\n\n* Overview\n\nEmbassies & Consulates\n\n* Embassies & Consulates \"Embassies & Consulates\")\n\n* Iranian Embassies & Consulates\n\n* Iran's UN Representation Offices\n\n* Foreign Embassies & Consulates in Tehran\n\n* Embassies & Consulates\n\nServices\n\n* Consular \"Consular\")\n\n* E-visa\n\n* Q & A\n\n* Overview of consular services\n\n* Students\n\n* Citizenship\n\n* Services \"Services\")\n\n* Investment Opportunities\n\n* Visit Iran\n\n* Consular\n\n* Services\n\nNews Room\n\n* News Room \"News Room\")\n\n* Statements\n\n* Individuals and entities in the sanctions list of the Islamic Republic of Iran\n\n* Events\n\n* Publications\n\n* News Room\n\n* Communication \"Communication\")\n\n* Contacts\n\n* Communication\n\nMultimedia\n\n* Pictures and videos \"Pictures and videos\")\n\n* Pictures\n\n* Videos\n\n* Pictures and videos\n\n{{ itemData.Title }}\n\n[](https://en.mfa.gov.ir/ \"home \")\n\nSearch [](https://en.mfa.gov.ir/portal/newsview/791053/Foreign-Ministry-Spokesperson-explains-FMs-Saturday-visit-to-Oman \"Search\")\n\n1. Home\n\n2. News\n\n3. Statements\n\n[](https://en.mfa.gov.ir/portal/newsview/791053/Foreign-Ministry-Spokesperson-explains-FMs-Saturday-visit-to-Oman)\n\n2026/07/12 - 12:39 [](https://en.mfa.gov.ir/portal/PrintNews/791053)\n\nView 806\n\nForeign Ministry Spokesperson explains FMs Saturday visit to Oman\n\nForeign Ministry Spokesperson Esmaeil Baghaei responding to reporters questions about the Iran–Oman talks held in Muscat on Saturday.\n\nForeign Ministry Spokesperson Esmaeil Baghaei, responding to reporters' questions about the Iran–Oman talks held in Muscat on Saturday, said that the meeting between the foreign ministers of Iran and Oman was aimed at coordinating between the two littoral states of the Strait of Hormuz regarding arrangements for the management of transit and navigation through the strategic waterway.\n\nHe said that the talks, which were also attended by legal and technical delegations from both countries, included discussions on ensuring the security and safety of navigation in the Strait of Hormuz, while respecting the sovereign rights of the two littoral states, the applicable rules of international law, and taking into account the provisions of Clause 5 of the Islamabad Memorandum of Understanding.\n\nThe Islamic Republic of Iran maintains that future arrangements governing transit through the Strait of Hormuz should be developed through consultations between the two littoral states, taking into consideration the developments of recent months, particularly the imposed US-Zionist regime war and its security implications for navigation in the Strait of Hormuz.\n\nOman and Iran agreed to continue their discussions at both the political and technical-legal levels with the aim of reaching a shared understanding on ensuring the security of navigation in the Strait of Hormuz.\n\nIt is noteworthy that, during part of the talks, a delegation from the Qatari government was present as a representative of one of the regional countries that has also served as a mediator in the US-Iran negotiations in recent months.\n\nAttachments\n\nویدئوها\n\nتصاویر\n\nصوت‌ها\n\nمتن دیدگاه\n\nشما در حال پاسخ به کامنت زیر هستید\n\nنظر شما با موفقیت ذخیره شد و پس از تایید نمایش داده خواهد شد\n\nنظرات کاربران\n\nتاکنون نظری ثبت نشده است\n\nYour Rate\n\nCurrentRate\n\nStatements\n\n[](https://en.mfa.gov.ir/portal/newsview/791086)\n\nForeign Ministry statement on US military aggression against Iran\n\n2026/07/13\n\n[](https://en.mfa.gov.ir/portal/newsview/790981)\n\nIran condemns terrorist attack in Pakistan calls for stronger regional cooperation against terrorism\n\n2026/07/10\n\n[](https://en.mfa.gov.ir/portal/newsview/790924)\n\nForeign Ministry Statement on the Aggressive Acts of the US Terrorist Military Against Iran Last Night\n\n2026/07/09\n\n[](https://en.mfa.gov.ir/portal/newsview/790919)\n\nIranian FM Thanks Iraqi People and Government for Hosting Funeral of Martyred Leader of the Islamic Revolution\n\n[](https://en.mfa.gov.ir/portal/newsview/790842)\n\nIran rejects Qatars allegation over reported incident involving Qatar-linked vessel in Strait of Hormuz\n\n2026/07/08\n\n[](javascript:void(0); \"Back to top\")\n\nIslamic Republic of Iran Ministry of Foreign Affairs\n\n[](https://www.facebook.com/Irimfa \"Facebook\")\n\n[](https://en.mfa.gov.ir/portal/viewpage/14750 \"Instagram\")\n\n[](https://en.mfa.gov.ir/portal/viewpage/14751 \"Twitter\")\n\n[](https://t.me/mfairan \"Telegram\")\n\nLinks\n\nOfficial Website of Supreme LeaderOfficial Website of the PresidentOfficial Website of GovernmentInstitute for Political and International StudiesEconomic Diplomacy Deputy\n\nquick access\n\nFeedback\n\nLast Update\n\n07/13/2026\n\nAdd.: Ministry of Foreign Affairs, Imam Khomeini St., Imam Khomeini Sq., Tehran, IRAN Call Center : 61151Email : info@mfa.gov.ir\n\n© All Rights Reserved for Ministry of Foreign Affairs of the Islamic Republic of Iran",
